{"LULL":[{"def":"To cause to rest by soothing influences; to compose; to calm; to soothe; to quiet.","pos":""}],"LULLABY":[{"def":"A song to quiet babes or lull them to sleep; that which quiets.","pos":""},{"def":"Hence: Good night; good-by.","pos":""}],"LULLER":[{"def":"One who, or that which, lulls.","pos":""}],"LULLINGLY":[{"def":"In a lulling manner; soothingly.","pos":""}]}